Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.00,0:00:10.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}字幕转换助手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.55,0:00:03.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k155}流動的水沒有形狀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.69,0:00:05.63,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k214}漂流的風找不到蹤跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.63,0:00:07.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k194}任何案件的推理都取決於心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.59,0:00:09.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k196}一堆令人嚮往的超級車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.63,0:00:10.46,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}天價的名車卻隱藏複雜的心思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.50,0:00:12.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k87}唯一揭開事情的真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.63,0:00:14.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k213}外表看似小孩，頭腦卻過於常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.63,0:00:16.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}他的名字就叫...名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.85,0:00:21.72,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k222}正因為你和我是不同的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.99,0:00:30.73,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}喜好不同 腳程與表達的方式也大異其趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.46,0:00:37.63,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}如今我們在兩人的記憶中正在漸漸褪色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.43,0:00:45.14,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我摸索過 卻開始探尋其他人與未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.27,0:00:52.28,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我比自己想像的活的更堅強 追尋一種特別的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.41,0:00:56.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}為難以應付的每一天所苦惱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.49,0:00:59.56,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}true heart for mystery eyes
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.69,0:01:07.03,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}為了不再迷惑 請別鬆開你的手腕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.30,0:01:09.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}即使是互相傷害的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.07,0:01:21.33,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我只是一直在迷惘的時空中找尋答案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.68,0:01:27.59,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}朝著下一個舞台 you take you way
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.48,0:01:31.86,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}請抱緊我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.39,0:01:38.86,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}I feel so all in secret life
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.67,0:01:46.42,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}197 超級汽車陷阱(前篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.33,0:01:50.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}好棒哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.37,0:01:52.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}還可以看到海呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.37,0:01:55.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}真的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.54,0:01:57.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}咦，叔叔呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.41,0:02:00.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k187}奇怪了，剛才還一起走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.54,0:02:05.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}喂~你們別顧著自已休息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.37,0:02:09.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真是的，雖然是一等獎的獎品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.62,0:02:11.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但是這種沒有交通工具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.45,0:02:14.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k183}又是深山裡的旅館，真的是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.50,0:02:16.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.41,0:02:19.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k191}爸爸，快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.50,0:02:22.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}旅館怎麼這麼遠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.54,0:02:25.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}根本完全不一樣嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.54,0:02:29.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}要是二等獎的刷刷鍋就好了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.62,0:02:30.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.37,0:02:34.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k75}討厭，不要說這種煞風景的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.66,0:02:36.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可是你告訴我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.45,0:02:38.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k179}什麼時候才能到那間旅館呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.41,0:02:41.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k196}就快到了，加油吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.58,0:02:46.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你看那間旅館應該就是了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.50,0:02:53.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}請在住宿卡上做登記
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.37,0:02:56.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}咦，毛利...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.58,0:03:00.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}毛利先生，房間是201號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.70,0:03:03.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}喂，這間旅館是很不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.58,0:03:07.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k288}不過沒考慮過做接送巴士嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.70,0:03:10.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不要這樣，爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.58,0:03:12.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k288}真是很對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.50,0:03:14.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k192}現在讓我帶你們到房間去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.50,0:03:19.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}麻煩你了，走吧柯南...咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.41,0:03:22.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}柯南 你在那裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.58,0:03:27.33,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}啊~好棒哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.50,0:03:31.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}好酷哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.54,0:03:34.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}柯南 你在這裡做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.62,0:03:36.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真是的，到處亂跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.50,0:03:39.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k188}你們看，好棒呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.62,0:03:42.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這裡有很多老式跑車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.58,0:03:44.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k296}真的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.50,0:03:48.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k192}這是捷克XK120
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.75,0:03:50.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這加長的車頭還有它的線條
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.50,0:03:52.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k175}是它的特徵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.54,0:03:55.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}看起來就像豹的身現一樣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.66,0:03:59.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}現在還是很多捷克迷的夢想車呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.70,0:04:01.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.50,0:04:04.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}還有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.66,0:04:07.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這是賓士300SL 卡恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.66,0:04:10.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}卡恩就像海鷗的翅膀一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.62,0:04:12.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k296}打開車門的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.54,0:04:17.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k192}就像海鷗展翅一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.41,0:04:18.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.41,0:04:22.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}咦，那是凱迪拉克吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.79,0:04:24.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}對 凱迪拉克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.54,0:04:26.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k175}是53年的CB
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.54,0:04:28.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}它擁有最棒的引擎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.58,0:04:31.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}也被稱為美國究極的車子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.66,0:04:34.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}因為只生產500輛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.66,0:04:37.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以很快就被買光了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.66,0:04:40.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}現在在同好之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.70,0:04:43.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這已經變成了傳說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.70,0:04:47.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}小男孩，你知道的還真詳細
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.79,0:04:51.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這裡是新成立的跑車展示窗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.79,0:04:53.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.62,0:04:56.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k183}本旅管的老闆是個超級跑車迷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.70,0:04:58.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}為了這個展示廳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.62,0:05:01.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k192}還特地將旅館做了改造呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.70,0:05:05.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}咦，最裡面是空的耶?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.83,0:05:07.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}恩，那個空間是用來放
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.58,0:05:10.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k175}社長的愛車法拉利迪諾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.70,0:05:12.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}咦，法拉利迪諾...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.62,0:05:16.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k192}不會是206GD吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.83,0:05:19.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就是....那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.70,0:05:20.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k287}太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.54,0:05:23.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k84}柯南，那是怎樣的車呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.75,0:05:26.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}全世界只有生產152輛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.70,0:05:28.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k295}就算現在想買
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.62,0:05:30.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k192}差不多已經是不可能的事情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.62,0:05:32.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}迪諾就是法拉利的創始者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.62,0:05:34.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}安澤法拉利的獨子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.62,0:05:37.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}亞倫迪諾的簡稱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.75,0:05:39.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}他在24歲就去世了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.66,0:05:42.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k191}不過生前參與開發的引擎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.75,0:05:45.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就裝置在這輛車子上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.75,0:05:49.83,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以安澤就將自己的愛子之名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.87,0:05:52.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}用在車子上面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.75,0:05:54.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k288}原來還有這個典故啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.62,0:05:56.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k187}勝昌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.62,0:05:58.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}接待人員離開接待處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.62,0:06:00.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}你到底在做什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.62,0:06:01.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.54,0:06:03.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k92}還有，客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.66,0:06:05.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k212}這個展示埸在明天開幕之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.62,0:06:09.83,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k196}是禁止進入的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.83,0:06:14.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.62,0:06:26.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那個客人，難道是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.62,0:06:38.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}社長，辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.79,0:06:41.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}雖然這輛車比生命還要寶貴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.83,0:06:43.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不過從東京開到這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.66,0:06:46.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k183}還是會累的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.83,0:06:48.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}社氝，其也的車子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.66,0:06:50.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k183}已經放在展示埸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.70,0:06:52.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}社長的車子也可以馬上開過去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.70,0:06:54.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}等等，不用那麼急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.70,0:06:58.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}今晚我想和它共度一晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.91,0:07:00.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}因為開始展示之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.75,0:07:04.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k184}就不能像這樣自由自在的駕駛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.91,0:07:07.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}社長，其實請看這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.79,0:07:10.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k288}嗯?偵探...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.83,0:07:14.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}怎麼回事?只有一張床啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.95,0:07:16.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}別那麼奢求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.75,0:07:19.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}免費住已經要謝天謝地了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.83,0:07:22.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這種床怎麼能睡的下三個人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.87,0:07:24.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我要他們幫我們換房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.75,0:07:26.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k188}有什麼關係，睡沙發就行了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.70,0:07:30.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k195}大叔還是那麼天真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.95,0:07:33.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}放心，包在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.87,0:07:36.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k292}明天下午三點就會開幕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.87,0:07:38.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以今晚是最後的機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.75,0:07:41.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k188}對，你不用擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.87,0:07:43.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}按照計劃去做就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.75,0:07:48.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k188}知道了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.66,0:07:50.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}柯南，你過來一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.75,0:07:52.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k209}放開我，小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.79,0:07:54.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}不要鬧了，爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.75,0:07:57.83,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k196}反正這旅館又沒人住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.87,0:07:59.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我一定要他們換房間給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.75,0:08:01.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k188}但是如果這樣做的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.79,0:08:03.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}可能會被收追加費用吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.79,0:08:05.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}而且如果再那麼吵的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.75,0:08:08.83,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k196}可能會被趕出這裡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.87,0:08:12.95,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.00,0:08:14.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.79,0:08:17.83,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k179}恐嚇信?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.87,0:08:18.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我看看...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.66,0:08:23.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k79}別開展示埸，不然要你後悔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.00,0:08:26.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那封恐嚇言是幾天前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.83,0:08:31.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}大家正在商量要怎麼處理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.04,0:08:32.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這封恐嚇信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.79,0:08:34.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k175}的確有點魄力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.83,0:08:37.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}這會不會是單純的惡作劇呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.91,0:08:39.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}如果是這樣就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.83,0:08:41.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k192}我希望你能在明天開幕之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.83,0:08:44.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}替我做護衛，可以嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.91,0:08:46.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我們想藉助名偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.79,0:08:49.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k188}毛利先生的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.95,0:08:52.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}有沒有報警?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.95,0:08:55.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}如果您願意答應的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.95,0:08:57.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我願意提供本旅館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.83,0:09:02.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k188}最豪華的這個房間給你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.04,0:09:03.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這貴賓房嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.83,0:09:05.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k179}爸爸...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.83,0:09:07.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}知道了，我接受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.83,0:09:09.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.83,0:09:11.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}這樣我也可以安心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.87,0:09:16.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}請大家就像坐在大船裡，放心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.75,0:09:33.83,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}對了，蘭小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.83,0:09:35.83,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k208}等用完晚餐之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.87,0:09:38.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}要不要坐我的車去游車河?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.00,0:09:41.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}呃，可以坐迪諾嗎?太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.00,0:09:44.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}叔叔，我也可以去嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.95,0:09:46.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k295}當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.91,0:09:51.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k196}爸爸，我也可以去嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.08,0:09:55.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真美味，這牛排
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.12,0:09:56.83,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}實在太好吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.87,0:09:58.83,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k175}喂...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.87,0:10:01.95,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}真好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.00,0:10:04.95,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我還要再來一盤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.00,0:10:06.83,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不好，撒到你了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.91,0:10:09.95,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k191}沒關係，我是服務人員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.04,0:10:12.95,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}爸爸，你喝太多了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.04,0:10:14.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}社長，不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.87,0:10:16.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k183}在展示埸的車子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.87,0:10:19.95,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}什...什麼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.04,0:10:21.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}別阻止  別阻止我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.91,0:10:23.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k187}冷靜點，大竹先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.91,0:10:24.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}別這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.79,0:10:27.95,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k88}別妨礙我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.04,0:10:32.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}放開我，隨我去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.12,0:10:33.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你不要亂來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.95,0:10:37.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k183}囉唆!我要毀掉這輛車子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.04,0:10:38.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}大竹先生，為什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.95,0:10:43.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k191}這不是你最寶貴的車子嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.16,0:10:43.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.87,0:10:47.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k71}呃，要傷害自己的車子?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.04,0:10:51.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}大竹先生，你也真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.20,0:10:54.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你怎麼可能會瞭解我的心情呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.08,0:10:57.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k288}到底是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.08,0:10:58.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}舉辦這種...這種展示埸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.91,0:11:03.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k183}我要毀掉它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.91,0:11:14.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這輛車子，53年的CB
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.95,0:11:18.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}是我的夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.08,0:11:19.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}為了朝著這個夢想前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.95,0:11:21.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k187}我從早做到晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.00,0:11:25.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k205}終於可以得到這輛車子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.08,0:11:26.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}既然這麼重要的車子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.00,0:11:28.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k192}為什麼還要毀掉它呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.00,0:11:32.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}既然要我放棄這輛車的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.08,0:11:35.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我情願親手將它給毀掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.08,0:11:35.83,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}...我是這樣想的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.87,0:11:39.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k79}放棄?怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.08,0:11:42.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}怎麼回事...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.12,0:11:45.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}問在那裡的寺泉就知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.12,0:11:48.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}寺泉先生，到底是怎麼回事 ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.12,0:11:51.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這實在是天大的誤會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.12,0:11:52.95,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}大竹先生，你應該感謝我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.00,0:11:56.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k188}不應該恨我才對的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.12,0:11:57.95,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你要我感謝你?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.00,0:11:59.95,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k188}要開這展示會的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.00,0:12:01.95,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}根本沒人會高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.00,0:12:03.95,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}除了你以外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.00,0:12:05.95,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}他說得沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.04,0:12:09.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}大竹先生怎麼會明白失去愛車的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.12,0:12:10.95,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我十分瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.04,0:12:15.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k192}沒有人會高興開這展示會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.91,0:12:16.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.95,0:12:20.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k104}對不起，請問你們是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.16,0:12:22.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我和大竹先生一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.04,0:12:26.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k188}必須放棄這賓士的相良新介
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.25,0:12:29.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我是龜岡丈二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.16,0:12:31.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k291}那車捷克的前一住主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.04,0:12:34.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k188}我們三人都是被那裡的寺泉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.16,0:12:37.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}把車子給騙走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.16,0:12:39.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你怎麼可以這樣說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.04,0:12:42.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k188}這是你們自食惡果啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.16,0:12:45.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你們說被騙...這到底是怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.16,0:12:47.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我們3人雖然是小公司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.04,0:12:50.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k188}但是 都是個經營者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.16,0:12:52.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我是旅行代理店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.04,0:12:54.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k188}我是不動產
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.04,0:12:56.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}我是汽車修理廠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.08,0:12:58.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}但是在這種不景氣的情況下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.08,0:13:00.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}大家都出現經營上的困難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.04,0:13:02.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k196}結果在那裡的寺泉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.08,0:13:04.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}就說以這些車子做抵押
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.04,0:13:07.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k196}願意借錢給我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.20,0:13:11.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}當然我們接受了他的提議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.29,0:13:14.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但這是個陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.20,0:13:17.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k291}我們是後來才知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.20,0:13:19.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}都是那個男人從中作梗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.08,0:13:21.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k188}搶走了我們的生意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.12,0:13:24.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}結果最後日期到了還是無法還錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.20,0:13:26.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}車子就這樣被搶走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.12,0:13:29.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k192}寺泉一開始就想搶走我們的目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.20,0:13:33.95,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以才用金錢讓我們中計
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.04,0:13:37.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你說得還真像是真的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.25,0:13:41.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你有證據證明我陷害你們嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.33,0:13:43.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}如果你們有時間去胡思亂想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.08,0:13:46.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k175}不如想怎麼還錢更好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.20,0:13:48.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}只要你們還錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.12,0:13:50.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k192}車子隨時都可以還給你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.12,0:13:52.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}你說什麼!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.12,0:13:54.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}啍，想嚇唬我也沒用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.12,0:13:57.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}原來如此，那封恐嚇信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.20,0:13:59.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}原來是你們寫的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.12,0:14:01.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k192}恐嚇信?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.12,0:14:02.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}那是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.00,0:14:04.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k88}別裝蒜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.12,0:14:05.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k212}不管你們怎麼阻止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.04,0:14:09.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k92}我都會如期開幕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.04,0:14:13.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.12,0:14:15.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k208}相良先生的鞋子...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.12,0:14:18.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}放心，包在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.25,0:14:22.33,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}明天下午三點就會舉行開幕典禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.37,0:14:25.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以今晚是最後的機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.29,0:14:28.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k292}對，不用擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.29,0:14:33.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}照計劃去做就對了，知道嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.25,0:14:40.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}請問相良先生住幾號房呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.25,0:14:42.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}202號房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.16,0:14:44.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k191}這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.20,0:14:46.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}怎麼，我的房間有什麼問題嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.16,0:14:48.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k196}不，是因為...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.16,0:14:51.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}300SL實在太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.29,0:14:56.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}想今晚跑去找你聊一聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.12,0:14:59.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}啊，今晚不行 我有事要做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.16,0:15:04.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}跟你沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.29,0:15:09.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}說...說得也對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.20,0:15:13.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}酒店服務?我們沒叫啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.33,0:15:15.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}會不會是搞錯了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.20,0:15:18.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k187}不，因為你們是社長的客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.33,0:15:21.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以這是本旅館送的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.33,0:15:23.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}如果還有什麼需要的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.20,0:15:24.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k187}請不用客氣的說出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.12,0:15:28.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k92}是嗎，那麼給我一瓶紅酒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.45,0:15:30.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}最好是波爾多的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.20,0:15:34.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k175}爸爸，不要這樣!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.45,0:15:40.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}對了，剛才很抱歉弄髒你的褲子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.20,0:15:44.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我己經換過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.45,0:15:47.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}迪諾的引擎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.37,0:15:51.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k292}的確聽到一些引擎的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.45,0:15:54.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不會錯，是迪諾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.33,0:15:59.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k288}真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.20,0:16:02.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}社長，這麼晚你要去哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.37,0:16:05.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}因為那些傢伙毀了我今天的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.33,0:16:07.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k296}我要出去一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.29,0:16:09.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k196}寺泉先生，今晚的霧很大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.25,0:16:11.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k196}還是不要出去比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.29,0:16:14.33,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}在這車子裡面總比和那些傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.37,0:16:19.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}住在同一個旅館裡面更加安全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.33,0:16:26.33,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}請小心駕駛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.37,0:16:31.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.33,0:16:53.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}經理，社長還沒有回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.54,0:16:56.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真是的，已經九點了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.41,0:16:59.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k287}社長到底跑到哪裡去了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.41,0:17:02.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}還沒有回來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.41,0:17:05.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真是拿他沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.41,0:17:09.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不過下午三點才開幕吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.54,0:17:12.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}應該還來得及吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.41,0:17:14.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k287}別開玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.29,0:17:16.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k188}迪諾還要擺到展示埸去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.33,0:17:19.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}下午我們也要開始接待客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.45,0:17:22.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不過完全沒有連絡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.41,0:17:24.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k296}這實在太奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.33,0:17:26.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k192}寺泉還沒有回來嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.33,0:17:29.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}龜岡先生 大竹先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.45,0:17:33.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}萬一遇到突發事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.37,0:17:35.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}今天大概無法進行開幕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.33,0:17:37.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k196}這是天譴  天譴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.37,0:17:41.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}社長先生有沒有帶手機?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.58,0:17:44.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}啊，對了，我完全忘記了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.45,0:17:48.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k287}讓我來告訴他別讓別人擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.58,0:17:52.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}好好的跟他說教一番
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.58,0:17:54.33,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}喂，是社長嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.33,0:17:57.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k175}是我，毛利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.50,0:17:59.33,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你現在在哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.37,0:18:02.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k187}啊...這裡是什麼地方?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.45,0:18:04.33,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}怎麼一片漆黑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.37,0:18:07.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k192}一片漆黑?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.50,0:18:10.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}喂，社長? 社長?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.45,0:18:12.33,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k295}怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.37,0:18:14.33,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k192}他用很痛苦的聲音說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.41,0:18:17.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}這裡是哪裡，怎麼一片漆黑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.45,0:18:19.33,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}接者就斷線了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.41,0:18:23.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k196}漆黑...外面大霧應該是白色的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.62,0:18:28.33,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}毛利先生，漆黑是...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.29,0:18:35.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}經理，已經十點了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.37,0:18:36.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k208}今天的準備工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.29,0:18:39.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k92}再不開始就來不及了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.54,0:18:42.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}也對，那就拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.50,0:18:47.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k296}好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.45,0:18:51.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}看來 今天的開幕典禮是開不成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.41,0:18:54.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k196}中止，一定是遭天譴了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.50,0:18:56.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.41,0:18:59.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k191}變成和恐嚇信一樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.50,0:19:02.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.50,0:19:07.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}小蘭?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.37,0:19:10.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}小蘭姊姊，小蘭姊姊在哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.54,0:19:14.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}柯南，我在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.66,0:19:19.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}小蘭姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.54,0:19:25.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}小蘭姊姊，怎麼了?沒事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.66,0:19:27.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}嗯，我沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.45,0:19:31.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k179}小蘭，怎麼了，小蘭?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.66,0:19:33.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}對不起，我出來散步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.50,0:19:35.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k184}結果在霧中突然有人叫我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.45,0:19:37.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k195}害我嚇了一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.45,0:19:40.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}你不是野田警衛嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.58,0:19:43.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你在這裡做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.54,0:19:45.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k296}其實是這位小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.45,0:19:47.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k191}在霧中正往懸崖方向走去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.45,0:19:49.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}我覺得很危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.45,0:19:51.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}才會叫住她的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.45,0:19:53.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}然後她突然大叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.45,0:19:55.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.45,0:19:58.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}真是令人擔心的女兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.62,0:20:00.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}啊，有車子的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.45,0:20:02.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k183}社長終於回來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.50,0:20:04.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k205}不，那聲音不是社長的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.50,0:20:07.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}是相良先生的車子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.58,0:20:12.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}呃?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.54,0:20:18.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}怎麼了，大家都在一起?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.62,0:20:21.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真的耶，聽聲音就知道是哪輛車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.58,0:20:24.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k296}實在太厲害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.62,0:20:27.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這裡的常客大部分都能認出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.62,0:20:31.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那麼我繼續去巡邏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.79,0:20:34.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}相良先生，你昨晚去哪裡了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.66,0:20:39.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k287}啊，到附近逛了一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.50,0:20:41.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}途中有沒有看到社長的車子?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.50,0:20:42.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.45,0:20:44.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k95}你退後一點，我要把車子開到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.54,0:20:49.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k209}停車埸去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.50,0:20:52.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}啊，經理，現在要展示迪諾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.54,0:20:55.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}可能已經來不及了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.62,0:20:57.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}嗯....
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.58,0:20:59.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k196}不管怎麼，現在最重要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.54,0:21:01.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k196}就是社長現在身在何處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.58,0:21:03.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}找不到他的話根本什麼也做不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.54,0:21:06.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k196}喂，不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.62,0:21:08.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}寺泉他...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.58,0:21:11.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k196}在車裡的寺泉樣子有點奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.66,0:21:16.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}呃! 什麼!?
