Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.75,0:21:30.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}社長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.45,0:21:32.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k70}快找醫生 快叫救護車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.58,0:21:37.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k213}沒用的  他已經死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.66,0:21:46.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}死因是二氧化碳中毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.83,0:21:48.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}因為引擎一直啟動者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.58,0:21:51.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k175}使的車內充滿廢氣瓦斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.70,0:21:53.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我想大概是廢氣瓦斯逆流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.58,0:21:56.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k188}跑進車子裡面了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.70,0:21:58.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這應該是意外死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.58,0:22:00.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k188}啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.58,0:22:02.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}窗戶有點微開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.58,0:22:06.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}這到底是...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.87,0:22:09.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}為什麼，為何窗戶會微開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.70,0:22:12.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k283}這真的是....
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.70,0:22:17.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}意外死亡嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.79,0:22:37.09,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不知道　該用什麼話語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.54,0:22:44.19,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}才能告訴你我真正的感覺呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.24,0:22:53.51,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}從那時起　不知過了多少季節
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.19,0:22:59.44,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}雖然時間無情地流逝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.16,0:23:06.94,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你卻總是　微笑地陪著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.84,0:23:17.19,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我沒對你說出口的  至今還有一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.34,0:23:22.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}Secret of my heart
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.34,0:23:22.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}請你不要懷疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.29,0:23:28.34,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}無論何時　只要還有少許未來的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.46,0:23:33.34,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真相　是緊握在手中的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.49,0:23:39.99,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}I can't say
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.49,0:23:39.99,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}I'm waiting for a chance
